dct_description_sm: Title taken from sheet 1. "Oct. 1927." Includes location map, key, streets and specials index, and text. Oriented with the north to the upper right. "3338". MAP copy 2: Bound into one three-post Sanborn binder. "New report, November 1943", "Additional index, October 1953" and "Correction record, 1954" -- Pasted on sheet 1. MAP copy 2: "22 - Additional sheet, October 1938" - Bound in at end.
